{"tid":1986052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國、法國：現在還不是進行調查的時候","createTime":"2020-04-23T14:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T20:48:32.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e27b78e6ffba9ee899a5912636779495df89bdf3","tid":1986052,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"法國：<br />\nMacron told Morrison now was not the time for an investigation, a French official said.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;He says he agrees that there have been some issues at the start, but that the urgency is for cohesion, that it is no time to talk about this, while reaffirming the need for transparency for all players, not only the WHO,&rdquo; an Elysee official told Reuters.<br />\n<br />\n英國：<br />\nA spokesman for Prime Minister Boris Johnson said there would be a time when Britain will have to look at the lessons to be learned from the crisis, but for now ministers were focused on fighting the pandemic.<br />\n<br />\n德國：<br />\nIn Berlin, the government confirmed that Merkel had spoken with Morrison on Tuesday. Last Friday, her spokesman said: &ldquo;The coronavirus appeared first in China. China has suffered a lot from the virus and did a lot to fight against spreading.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n路透社：<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-australia/australia-seeks-probe-into-coronavirus-spread-france-and-uk-say-now-not-the-time-idUSKCN22401K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-australia%2Faustralia-seeks-probe-into-coronavirus-spread-france-and-uk-say-now-not-the-time-idUSKCN22401K&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=a852f73c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-australia%2Faustralia-seeks-probe-into-coronavirus-spread-france-and-uk-say-now-not-the-time-idUSKCN22401K&h=3a8894ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reut